<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ سُورَةِ الْمَاعُون<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٧٧:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {أَرَأَيْتَ الَّذِي يُكَذِّبُ بِالدِّينِ <span class="c2">(١)</span> فَذَلِكَ الَّذِي يَدُعُّ الْيَتِيمَ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَلَا يَحُضُّ عَلَى طَعَامِ الْمِسْكِينِ <span class="c2">(٣)</span> فَوَيْلٌ لِلْمُصَلِّينَ <span class="c2">(٤)</span> الَّذِينَ هُمْ عَنْ صَلَاتِهِمْ سَاهُونَ <span class="c2">(٥)</span> الَّذِينَ هُمْ يُرَاءُونَ <span class="c2">(٦)</span> وَيَمْنَعُونَ الْمَاعُونَ <span class="c2">(٧)</span>} <span class="c4">[الماعون: ١ - ٧]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{يَدُعُّ}</span>: <span class="c1">" يَدْفَعُ عَنْ حَقِّهِ،<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> هُوَ مِنْ دَعَعْتُ "</span>، <span class="c3">{يَوْمَ يُدَعُّونَ}</span> <span class="c4">[الطور: ١٣]</span>: <span class="c2">«يُدْفَعُونَ»</span>،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{سَاهُونَ}</span>: <span class="c2">«لاَهُونَ»</span>،<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{المَاعُونَ}</span>: <span class="c1">" المَعْرُوفَ كُلُّهُ،<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ بَعْضُ العَرَبِ:</span> المَاعُونُ: المَاءُ "<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ عِكْرِمَةُ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَعْلاَهَا: الزَّكَاةُ المَفْرُوضَةُ،<span class="c5"> وَأَدْنَاهَا:</span> عَارِيَّةُ المَتَاعِ»</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>